    "Recall the ladder where the top of the ladder represents your best possible life and the bottom of the ladder represents your worst possible life.",
    "On which step of the ladder do you personally feel that you would like to stand?",
    "Cantril no Ladder Please imagine a scale with values from 0 at the bottom to 10 at the top.",
    "Number 10 represents the best possible life for you and 0 represents the worst possible life for you.",
    "On which number of the scale would you say you personally feel you are at this time?"
  ]
